Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:33.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい風のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描くよ　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:42.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.71,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さなことで揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.31,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱い自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣きたいときだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:55.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:00.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしだけにできることがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:09.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめないよ　君を守り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:15.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないスピードで想いがあふれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりも輝いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星がみえない日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:27.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光はある　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:30.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じること…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い、　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:41.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの空で逢えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.28,0:00:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================opcn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:33.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}炫目的風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描繪你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:42.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}變得坦率的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因小事而動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軟弱的自己令我懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:55.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仰頭忍淚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:00.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必定有唯有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:09.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不言棄 一直守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:15.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思念正以停不下的速度膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願比任何人都耀目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使夜空沒有繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:27.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亦會有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:30.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往未來的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:41.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能在那片天空相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要向大家介紹一位插班生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多關照 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以叫我夏爾魯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 就跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然是她的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2\blur4\pos(455,127)\fs26\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}室友是金髮貴公子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2\blur4\pos(512,100)\fs17\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}(Gentle)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣唰地一下過去以後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再辟哩啪啦地動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱約能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠的就是感覺啊 感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥? 為啥不明白啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦的時候 右半身斜向上 往前方5度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴避時要往後方2O度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就照實說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽講啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說明一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 右斜向前傾5度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我對戰一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟白式戰一場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾魯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢 過後再教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 織斑跟迪諾亞似乎要幹一場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 迪諾亞的專用機是「Rafale Revive」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國的第二世代IS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始了哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏之所以赢不了的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純沒有掌握射擊武器的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自以為還是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台白式沒有後付武裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(374,325)\fs16}（Equalizer）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 似乎沒有空餘的擴張領域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,325)\fs16}（Bus Slot）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可能是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的One-Off Ability用了這些容量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,325)\fs16}（唯一特殊才能）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One-Off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS和操縱者在最佳狀態配合下之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然發生的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白式就是「零落白夜」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的說明真是淺顯易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 明明不聽我的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說得那麼白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我那有條有理的說明有什麼不滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這「零落白夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是連護盾能量都用來攻擊 超胡來的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟織斑老師操縱過的IS同樣的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算是姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未必能使同樣的招數啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們稍微練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用不了其他人的裝備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一般情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是所有者進行使用許諾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,325)\fs16}（Unlock）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有備案的人都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣拿槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾緊腋窩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後左腕往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係是不是好過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想 就是一個「快」字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 德國的是第三世代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在他們國内還在試運行階段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉·博迪薇希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 就是那傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇了一夏一耳光的德國代表候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎也是專用機擁有者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼事情就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我戰一場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕 沒有戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有 但我有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必急著現在打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到班級對抗賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來就動手 德國人的沸點真夠低的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區法國的第二世代機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢跟我對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟比到目前還沒能量產
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國的第三世代要靈活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的學生 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 今天就暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人跟你之間發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛才多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦 夏爾魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不先在這裡淋個澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼抗拒跟我一起換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也一起換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然是她的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答我 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我重複太多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自己的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這塊極東之地 又能有什麼職責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次到我們德國執教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 根本發揮不到您一半的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這學園的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不值得教官去教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺乏危機感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤以為IS是時髦之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值得教官花費時間在那種人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話別說太過了 丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段時間不見 變得很自大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15歲就一副唯我獨尊的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人不敢恭維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回宿舍去 我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的男生 在偷聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常癖好可不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為啥這麼說我啊 千冬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校要叫織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間做無聊事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去自主訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 月底的競技賽 估計第一場就要敗退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才拉烏拉那傢伙說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認同我是千冬姐的弟弟那句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為我令你錯過了衛冕冠軍的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:09:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二屆Mondo Grosso-IS世界大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決賽那天 我被人綁架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今還不知道出於什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被綁住禁錮在一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我的 正是放棄了決賽趕來的千冬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果千冬姐不戰而敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都確信她能衛冕 寄予厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她的棄權引發了一場風波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 德軍提供了禁錮我的地點消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了還這個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當了一年多的德軍IS部隊教官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都因為我沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個廢柴弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一味地受千冬姐保護了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 夏爾魯回来了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾魯 沐浴液用完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這是沐浴液…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙好燙 燙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都紅了 真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒啥大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別說這個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏真色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥說我色啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥要裝男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡要我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家…迪諾亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我爸是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他直接命令我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是爸爸正室的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直都跟爸爸分開住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前我被接了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 媽媽去世那時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪諾亞家的人就接我過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來在接受各種檢查的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了我很適合當IS操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 雖然是非正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當了試驗操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我只見過兩次爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊天的時間 還不夠一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在後來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司陷入經營危機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪諾亞公司的量產IS不是有世界第三的市場份額嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯 但Revive終歸是第二世代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在IS的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三世代開發已經成為主流了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞和拉烏拉轉進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計都是為了取得機體開發數據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡也有著手進行第三世代的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻不能成形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 開發許可會被剝奪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟你裝男人有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引世人注目的廣告塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 同是男生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也容易跟在日本出現的特異案例接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而能獲取使用機和操縱者的資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我被派來竊取你的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出真相之後 人也輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 抱歉一直都在騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 當然不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有父母 孩子就不會出生 道理是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不代表 他們就能為所欲為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟千冬姐也是被父母拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別說我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今也不想見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你以後要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了我是女兒身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被召回國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判得輕的話 估計是坐牢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就留在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吭聲的話 肯定不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸和公司應該都出不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS學園特記事項
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本學園學生 在校期間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不歸屬於任何國家 組織和團體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 在這學園裡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有三年時間你會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這段時間 想出解決辦法就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特記事項 有55個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣 也是很勤奮好學的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你維護我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸 胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部快露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼在意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想看?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏真色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是啦 為啥我就色了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像沒去吃晚飯 是不是不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 我進來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 夏爾魯好像有點感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正幫他蓋被子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帶一夏走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好也沒吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一·起·去吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃個晚飯有必要挽著手臂貼那麼緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 男性護送淑女是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話 似乎是我被護送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也跟著去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚飯有點沒吃飽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 箒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多會迅速增重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不用你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會練居合斬 消耗卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這把是真刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性護送淑女是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別這樣很不方便走路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個狀況 你就不會說點別的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不到自己的幸福 連狗都不如哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶飯回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會用筷子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是有練習過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我去拿叉子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾魯 我覺得你應該多向人撒撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個勁地客氣只會吃虧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧 就從依賴我開始怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏餵我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說可以撒嬌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 男子漢說一不二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一口想吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來了 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 飯粒粘臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那份無比的強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是我的目標 也是存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給教官留下污點的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論用什麼手段 都要剷除你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競技場有人開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 誰跟誰打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方是塞西莉亞和凰鈴音的強強聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是那個拉烏拉·博迪薇希
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一是不是太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不過情況很古怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 Blue Days/Red Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好見識一下 第三世代機的實力吧
